{"type": "article", "id": 11537, "title": "悬浮式唱片留声机", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-02T11:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000033BzGN2pH4WEQ7dxPC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自芝加哥的 Gramovox 公司推出的一款悬浮式唱片留声机，顾名思义，它可以让唱片“站起来”播放音乐。它通过一条硅胶皮带驱动唱片旋转，适用于每分 33 ⅓ 转和 45 转两种类型。同时，底座采用优质木材，颜色清淡优雅。对于都市里面黑胶爱好者来讲，这样的设计既节省空间，又现代感十足。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gramovox/floating-recordtm-vertical-turntable\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详情。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135658g49Y3BaX5WrjCmuG.jpg\" width=\"679\" height=\"380\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55964654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135701XO83UCxLQvIBA1Ge.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135705yTNA8lPU1iaojWxR.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135706OcLZ9hlsx3V6UR0B.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135706XbR5CWDwdKYclhmI.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}